com.example.dinim3akalpha001.javascript.JavaFxWebEngine
All Implemented Interfaces:
IWebEngine
public class JavaFxWebEngine extends Object implements IWebEngine
This class provides an implementation of the IWebEngine interface utilizing a javafx.scene.web.WebEngine as the underlying engine.
